    <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">The W3C has a description of the use of the IETF language subtags at: http:// www .w3 .org/ International/ articles/ language -tags/ Overview .en .php</skos:scopeNote>
    <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">RFC 5646 requires the extension identifiers to be prefixed by a single character that identifies the registration authority that has registered the extension</skos:scopeNote>
    <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">IANA maintains a registry of language subtags at: http:// www .iana .org/ assignments/ language -subtag -registry</skos:scopeNote>
